title: Fifty Shades Darker Behind-The-Scenes Video Entertainment
text: Wondering when you can watch Fifty Shades Darker in the comfort of your own home? Universal Pictures has announced that the latest Fifty Shades of Grey film will be available on Digital HD on April 25 and 4K Ultra HD, Blu-ray, DVD, and On Demand on May 9. In addition to the extended, unrated version of Fifty Shades Darker , you'll get a sneak peek at the final film, Fifty Shades Freed , and a behind-the-scenes look at Jamie Dornan and Dakota Johnson on the set. Take a look at the clip now, and check out the whole cast of Fifty Shades Freed .
